text: Methoxamine is an α1-adrenergic receptor agonist, somewhat similar in structure to butaxamine and 2,5-DMA. It is no longer marketed.. == See also == * Sertraline * Phenylephrine * Synephrine * phentolamine == References == Category:Alpha-adrenergic agonists Category:Substituted amphetamines Category:Phenol ethers
title: Methoxamine
